  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior/ Security Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>What’s on Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mission: Provide compassionate, excellent and holistic healthcare. Tagline:- <strong>Serve all with Love</strong></li>\n  <li>Company: Guided by Catholic values, as a missionary not-for-profit hospital, we reach out and serve all our patients and visitors with love, continue to make private healthcare accessible to our community by providing reasonable price points and bill transparency. We continue to be progressive to better serve current and future generations.</li>\n  <li>Values: <strong>Compassion, Humility, Integrity, Respect and Peace (CHIRP).</strong></li>\n  <li>Work Satisfaction: An impactful role in shaping a high performing &amp; engaging culture.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Who We Need</strong></p>\n<p>Your key responsibilities are:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct regular patrols of the premises to ensure the security, safety and wellbeing.</li>\n  <li>Investigate and report all security breaches and building defect immediately.</li>\n  <li>Respond to emergency and provide necessary actions when required.</li>\n  <li>Control traffic by directing drivers / SCDF officers when applicable.</li>\n  <li>Assist in maintaining orderly parking of vehicles in the hospital premises.</li>\n  <li>Able to investigate and deal with conflict situations that occur within the hospital premises in an appropriate manner.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How to Succeed</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To perform 3 rotating shifts on 6-day work week including public holidays and weekends.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of relevant working experience.</li>\n  <li>Possesses a valid Police License Regulatory Department (PLRD) license.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Free Shuttle bus service from Bishan and Caldecott MRT station</li>\n  <li>Subsidised staff meals</li>\n  <li>AWS &amp; Variable bonus</li>\n</ul>",
